<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CONTENT id="_3793153_1"><TITLE value="Session 13"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884683_1" alt="" width="508" height="316" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Introduction&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div&gt;During this session we will investigate the frameworks designed to help identify vulnerabilties and improve cyber defences.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=369FyDCjecg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;The BIGGEST Software Supply Chain Attack in History - Threat Wire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DxMHGRKJNs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; (4.5 min)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.aph.gov.au/Parliamentary_Business/Bills_Legislation/Bills_Search_Results/Result?bId=r7250" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Cyber Security Bill 2024 – Parliament of Australia (aph.gov.au)&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Topic&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Managing the cyber security of any sized organisation is generally a daunting prospect.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Each organisation has different requirements and presents different vulnerabilities - even when the organisations in question may have similar network infrastructures.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;In order to deal with these challenges, various frameworks have been developed to assist the organisation's cyber defence personnel.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;During this session we will i&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;nvestigate the current Cyber Security Frameworks (CSF), focussing on:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;ISO 27000 series (see Session 8)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;NIST&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Essential Eight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Review the powerpoint, and the supplied video on NIST.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Portfolio Tasks&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Complete outstanding work&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
